@host = https://localhost:5010

### Health Check
GET {{host}}/api/balance/health
Accept: application/json

### Get All Customer Balances
GET {{host}}/api/balance/balances
Accept: application/json

### Get Balance for a Specific Customer
GET {{host}}/api/balance/balances/CUST-001
Accept: application/json

### Get Consumer Metrics (partitions, offsets)
GET {{host}}/api/balance/metrics
Accept: application/json

### Get Rebalancing History
GET {{host}}/api/balance/rebalancing-history
Accept: application/json
